text: The 2018 World Cup Taekwondo Team Championships was the 10th edition of the World Cup Taekwondo Team Championships, and was held in Fujairah, United Arab Emirates from November 24 to November 25, 2018. ==Medalists== {| |- |rowspan=2|Men |rowspan=2| Soroush Ahmadi Sina Bahrami Mirhashem Hosseini Mehdi Khodabakhshi Abolfazl Yaghoubi |rowspan=2| Dmitry Artyukhov Anton Kotkov Sarmat Tsakoev Vladislav Yugay Andrey Zemledeltsev | Milad Beigi Payam Ghobadi Radik Isayev Gashim Magomedov Mahammad Mammadov |- | Rakhym Adilkhanov Yerassyl Kaiyrbek Nurlan Myrzabayev Yeldos Yskak Ruslan Zhaparov |- |rowspan=2|Women |rowspan=2| Luo Zongshi Wenren Yuntao Zhang Mengyu Zheng Shuyin Zhou Lijun |rowspan=2| Bouma Ferimata Coulibaly Banassa Diomandé Marie Frédérique Ekpitini Ruth Gbagbi Aminata Traoré | Olga Ivanova Yulia Turutina Yulia Zaitseva Karina Zhdanova Arina Zhivotkova |- | Yasmina Aziez Althéa Laurin Haby Niaré Estelle Vander-Zwalm Magda Wiet-Hénin |- |rowspan=2|Mixed |rowspan=2| Kadyrbech Daurov Yury Kirichenko Ekaterina Derbeneva Polina Khan |rowspan=2| Hasan Can Lazoğlu Yunus Sarı Sude Bulut İkra Kayır | Kazybek Baktiyaruly Smaiyl Duisebay Fariza Aldangorova Cansel Deniz |- | Cheick Sallah Cissé Lamine Sidibé Marie Frédérique Ekpitini Ruth Gbagbi |} ==Men== ===Preliminary round=== ====Group A==== ====Group B==== ===Knockout round=== ==Women== ===Preliminary round=== ====Group A==== ====Group B==== ===Knockout round=== ==Mixed== ==References== ==External links== *Official website World Cup Category:World Cup Taekwondo Team Championships Taekwondo Championships Taekwondo
